    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> in a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp</span>]<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Toss the <strong>salad</strong> in the dressing</p>",
